00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.120
to massacre the borders.

00:03:51.159 --> 00:03:52.560
Yet she did not.

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.639
That may be true,

00:03:56.159 --> 00:03:58.360
but who can guarantee it now?

00:03:59.039 --> 00:03:59.840
I can.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.719
I will bear witness.

00:04:02.199 --> 00:04:03.000
This is…

