00:06:19.519 --> 00:06:20.639
How could I blame you?

00:06:21.800 --> 00:06:22.600
Besides,

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:28.439
have you forgotten?

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.800
We are allies now.

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:34.480
This token was given to me
by Your Highness' own hand.

00:06:35.300 --> 00:06:36.399
There is no taking it back.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:38.600
You...

00:06:39.639 --> 00:06:41.399
You went through great trouble

00:06:41.480 --> 00:06:42.439
to see me.

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:46.160
Surely not for small talk.

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:48.959
How could your safety
ever be small talk?

00:06:55.079 --> 00:06:55.879
But I do

00:06:57.879 --> 00:06:59.199
have news to report.

00:07:02.399 --> 00:07:03.400
