00:08:18.959 --> 00:08:20.759
I am not as noble as you imagine.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:22.639
Besides,

00:08:23.959 --> 00:08:25.160
I still have you.

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:30.360
I trust myself,

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:32.559
and I trust you.

00:08:57.480 --> 00:08:57.919
I

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:01.279
